            "title": "商米IPO在港售股超購2002倍 1手中籤率5% 股份今掛牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">商米科技(06810)昨晚公布招股結果，在港公開售股部份獲2003.16倍認購，1手中籤率5%；國際配售也有7.91倍認購。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"商米科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Sunmi-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"商米科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Sunmi-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">商米科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股將於今日掛牌，昨天傍晚暗盤成功高收。輝立交易平台顯示，商米暗盤收報93.65元，較招股價高2.77倍；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤收市價95元，更高於招股價2.82倍。</p>\n</div>",
